# Assets - Icons

This folder contains custom icons and favicons for the Açaí Premium website.

## Current Implementation

The website uses icons from:
- **Phosphor Icons** (via CDN): `https://unpkg.com/@phosphor-icons/web`
- **Font Awesome** (via CDN): `https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css`

## Favicon

Currently using a generated favicon. To add a custom favicon:
1. Add `favicon.png` to this folder
2. Update the link in index.html:
   ```html
   <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/icons/favicon.png">
   ```

## Custom Icons

To add custom SVG icons:
1. Add SVG files to this folder
2. Reference them in CSS or HTML as needed
